Global Modular Refinery Market Insights
Modular Refinery Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 9.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Modular Refinery Market Overview
The global modular refinery market is experiencing significant growth, driven by the increasing demand for cost-effective and flexible refining solutions. As of 2024, the market value is estimated at USD 1.5 billion and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 8.3% over the next five years. The adoption of modular refineries is being fueled by the need for localized refining operations, energy security, and the reduction of capital investment required for traditional large-scale refineries. The modular refinery market is anticipated to play a key role in improving energy infrastructure across developing regions and in areas with limited access to large refining plants.

